== English ==
=== Etymology ===
* The term was coined as an [[insidious]] extension of the [[Black Legend]]. 
===Proper noun===
'''White Legend'''
# The term [[purport]]s to counterbalance the defamatory anti-Hispanic [[Black Legend]] (Spanish: [[Leyenda Negra]]). It is an insidious aspect of the Black Legend in that it characterizes documented historical facts favorable to [[Hispanic]]s as exaggerated praise and therefore suspect.

